14
00:00:01,220 --> 00:00:02,990
《塞勒姆》前情提要
Previously on "Salem"...

15
00:00:03,550 --> 00:00:04,790
"偉大的儀式"
Ritum magni.

16
00:00:05,150 --> 00:00:06,070
大祭典
The grand rite?

17
00:00:06,080 --> 00:00:08,340
這里提到了這個物件 "惡靈" 
It says this object, this "Malum,"

18
00:00:08,340 --> 00:00:09,260
在歷史上
is thought to be present

19
00:00:09,270 --> 00:00:11,280
每次大祭典中都會出現
at every grand rite throughout history.

20
00:00:11,280 --> 00:00:12,750
這是邪惡之物
This object is evil.

21
00:00:13,890 --> 00:00:16,460
它將使大地生靈涂炭  以迎惡魔回歸
It consecrates the earth for the devil's return.

22
00:00:16,460 --> 00:00:18,820
這是一個包裹  那一定有收件人
It was here for delivery. Someone was expecting it.

23
00:00:18,820 --> 00:00:20,590
就是說其他人都已背叛我了
So the others have turned on me.

24
00:00:20,590 --> 00:00:21,620
沒錯
Yes.

25
00:00:21,620 --> 00:00:23,010
每個人
Each and every one.

26
00:00:23,010 --> 00:00:23,800
蘿絲
Rose?

27
00:00:23,980 --> 00:00:24,970
每個人
Everyone.

28
00:00:25,370 --> 00:00:27,760
如果你希望約翰·奧登活著
If you wish for John Alden to live,

29
00:00:27,760 --> 00:00:29,950
你就必須完成大祭典
you will complete the grand rite.

30
00:00:29,950 --> 00:00:31,500
什么是大祭典
What is the grand rite?

31
00:00:35,730 --> 00:00:38,970
你們以為可以把我像垂線木偶一樣任意擺布嗎
You think you can dangle me like a puppet?

32
00:00:38,970 --> 00:00:43,060
你們才是木偶  你們所有人  木偶
You're the puppets, all of you -- puppets!

33
00:00:43,060 --> 00:00:43,590
我記得你說過
I thought you said

34
00:00:43,590 --> 00:00:45,720
土星會迫使她說出真相
Saturn would compel her to speak the truth.

35
00:00:45,720 --> 00:00:46,580
沒錯
It did.

36
00:00:46,960 --> 00:00:48,970
有時候  真相就是一個謎語
Sometimes the truth is a riddle.

37
00:00:48,970 --> 00:00:49,600
那謎底呢
And the answer?

38
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:52,160
我得好好思索一番
I must think and then think again.

39
00:00:55,820 --> 00:00:56,550
父親
Father?

40
00:01:00,250 --> 00:01:01,780
來吧  孩子
Come, child.

41
00:01:01,780 --> 00:01:03,970
是時候來談談你父親的事了
It's time we talked about your father.

42
00:01:04,260 --> 00:01:07,230
你未經我同意把惡靈帶到了塞勒姆
You brought the malum to Salem behind my back.

43
00:01:35,420 --> 00:01:37,280
他們將無一幸免
Not one of them will survive.

44
00:01:38,990 --> 00:01:40,940
照這樣下去  我們也是一樣
Nor the rest of us, at this rate.

45
00:01:42,990 --> 00:01:44,660
我們已被困十天
10 days becalmed.

46
00:01:46,140 --> 00:01:48,140
水和食物快消耗光了
Nearly out of food and water.

47
00:01:48,140 --> 00:01:49,340
除非借助東風
We've no hope 

48
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:51,940
否則我們毫無希望
unless we catch the wind.

49
00:01:54,930 --> 00:01:57,600
我們要借助的不是東風  船長
It is not the wind that we must catch, captain.

50
00:01:59,730 --> 00:02:01,220
是巫師
It is a witch.

51
00:02:01,220 --> 00:02:04,110
看著我  小姑娘
Girl, look at me.

52
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:08,670
我們已經調查過所有你認為是巫師的
We have searched every passenger and crew member

53
00:02:09,290 --> 00:02:11,520
乘客和船員
for your supposed witches.

54
00:02:12,290 --> 00:02:13,670
毫無發現
None were found.

55
00:02:13,670 --> 00:02:15,390
船上有個巫師
There is a witch on this ship.

56
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,300
你能懂我意思嗎  船長
You understand me, captain?

57
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:26,400
為了阻止我  他將殺光所有船上的人員
The witch will kill everyone aboard in order to stop me.

58
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:29,410
我們會找出這個巫師的
We will find the witch.

59
00:02:35,190 --> 00:02:36,650
別出錯
Make no mistake.

60
00:02:37,410 --> 00:02:39,310
否則下一個就是你
It could just as well be your head.

61
00:02:39,760 --> 00:02:42,170
蘿絲未經我同意把惡靈帶到了這兒
Rose brought the malum here behind my back

62
00:02:42,740 --> 00:02:44,800
想要背著我完成大祭典
to complete the grand rite without me.

63
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:47,650
是誰的提議讓清教徒的矛頭
Whose idea was it to turn the puritans' hatred

64
00:02:47,650 --> 00:02:49,060
對準他們自己
against themselves?

65
00:02:49,870 --> 00:02:50,940
利用他們來完成
To use them to achieve

66
00:02:50,940 --> 00:02:53,430
諸世紀以來的第一場大祭典
the first grand rite in centuries?

67
00:02:53,950 --> 00:02:55,400
是誰讓大祭典得以實現
Who made that possible?

68
00:02:56,780 --> 00:02:57,510
是我
Me.

69
00:02:59,150 --> 00:03:02,690
而你和那個賤人卻不相信我
Yet you and that foul bitch mistrusted me.

70
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:06,080
你罪加一等  因為你低估了我
And much worse for you, you underestimated me.

71
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,480
但殺了死亡之神
But killing the Samhain,

72
00:03:09,510 --> 00:03:11,570
你知道這樣做有多嚴重嗎
do you have any idea what you've done?

73
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:14,230
問題不是
The question

74
00:03:14,230 --> 00:03:17,220
我有沒有意識到它的嚴重性
is not whether I understand what I have done,

75
00:03:17,630 --> 00:03:21,400
而是你有沒有意識到你現在該干什么
but whether you understand what you must now do.

76
00:03:25,340 --> 00:03:26,140
我明白了
I do.

77
00:03:28,370 --> 00:03:30,620
你擁有了古老的權利
You have claimed the ancient right.

78
00:03:32,010 --> 00:03:34,170
我奉你為新任的死亡之神
I recognize you as the new Samhain.

79
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:50,970
我愿意臣服于你的力量  為你浴血奮戰
I will honor and obey your power, earned in blood,

80
00:03:52,510 --> 00:03:54,810
我會傳話給其他人的
and share the word with the rest of the hive.

81
00:03:58,660 --> 00:04:00,940
狩獵滿月即將來臨
Full hunter's moon is soon upon us.

82
00:04:01,770 --> 00:04:03,640
屆時我們還需要八名死者
We need eight more dead by then.

83
00:04:05,550 --> 00:04:06,900
我有個計劃...
And I have a plan...

84
00:04:09,050 --> 00:04:13,020
只需一著  就能讓我們離目標咫尺之遙
to put us within reach of our goal with one single move.

85
00:04:13,940 --> 00:04:16,860
一次獲得三個祭品
Three sacrificed all at once.

86
00:04:17,310 --> 00:04:18,640
但你給我聽清楚了
But mark me well --

87
00:04:19,550 --> 00:04:23,840
如果任何人敢違背我的意愿  我唯你是問
If anyone goes behind my back, I hold you responsible.

88
00:04:24,770 --> 00:04:26,070
你會付出代價的
You will pay for it,

89
00:04:26,770 --> 00:04:28,730
不然就是你的妻子和女兒
or your wife and sweet daughter will.

90
00:04:39,260 --> 00:04:42,130
*擂我戰鼓*
*Pound me the witch drums*

91
00:04:42,130 --> 00:04:43,390
*鼓鳴震天*
*Witch drums*

92
00:04:43,390 --> 00:04:46,790
*擂我戰鼓*
*Pound me the witch drums*

93
00:04:47,260 --> 00:04:50,130
*擂我戰鼓*
*Pound me the witch drums*

94
00:04:50,130 --> 00:04:51,310
*鼓鳴震天*
*The witch drums*

95
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:53,840
*寧入地獄*
*Better pray for hell*

96
00:04:53,840 --> 00:04:59,900
*不留人間*
*Not hallelujah*

97
00:05:20,050 --> 00:05:21,190
間諜
A spy?

98
00:05:24,210 --> 00:05:25,150
什么意思
What do you mean?

99
00:05:27,820 --> 00:05:29,290
他在為法國人賣命嗎
Is he working for the French?

100
00:05:29,290 --> 00:05:30,040
不
No!

101
00:05:31,530 --> 00:05:32,810
當然不是
Of course not.

102
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,870
我不應該告訴你的
I should have said nothing.

103
00:05:37,470 --> 00:05:41,970
但你的疑心遲早會致我們于死地
But your infernal snooping only endangers us all.

104
00:05:41,970 --> 00:05:46,070
你父親是個秘密間諜
Your father is a confidential agent.

105
00:05:46,390 --> 00:05:48,130
他只是偶爾會為一個
He makes very occasional reports

106
00:05:48,130 --> 00:05:50,630
外國勢力機構提供一些情報
to agents representing another foreign power.

107
00:05:50,630 --> 00:05:53,590
是誰  他為什么要這樣做
Then who? And why?

108
00:05:53,590 --> 00:05:56,530
是誰重要嗎
What does it matter to whom your father speaks?

109
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:59,570
都是政治而已  親愛的
It's just politics, dear.

110
00:05:59,570 --> 00:06:00,950
沒什么大不了的
Of no import.

111
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:02,190
沒什么大不了
No import?

112
00:06:02,730 --> 00:06:06,360
你是說我父親是個叛國賊這沒什么大不了的嗎
That my father is a traitor is of no import?!

113
00:06:07,130 --> 00:06:08,150
不許你這么說
Never say that.

114
00:06:08,150 --> 00:06:09,760
你父親不是叛國賊
Your father is not a traitor.

115
00:06:09,760 --> 00:06:12,340
他是一個有著崇高理想的人
He is a man of the highest ideals!

116
00:06:12,350 --> 00:06:15,650
他所做的一切都是為了你
Everything your father he does, he does for you.

117
00:06:17,080 --> 00:06:20,710
為了你好  你少插手他的事情
Keep out of his affairs for your own good.

118
00:06:20,710 --> 00:06:24,300
你少糊弄我了  母親
I am utterly unconvinced by your story, mother.

119
00:06:24,710 --> 00:06:27,740
他就這么突然消失在我眼前
He seemed to vanish before my eyes.

120
00:06:28,420 --> 00:06:30,260
我不會道歉的
I make no apologies.

121
00:06:31,390 --> 00:06:34,440
我絕不會無視眼前所發生的一切
And I choose to walk through life with my eyes open.

122
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,170
就像你一樣
Unlike you.

123
00:06:38,340 --> 00:06:41,600
我知道你覺得我是個完全沒主見的蠢女人
I know you think me a stupid woman with no curiosity,

124
00:06:42,540 --> 00:06:44,610
但你不明白
but you don't understand.

125
00:06:48,860 --> 00:06:51,030
問題是一旦你知道真相
The problem with knowing things

126
00:06:52,020 --> 00:06:54,240
你就再也無法視而不見
is that you can never unknow them.

127
00:07:21,950 --> 00:07:23,270
來了嗎
Has it arrived?

128
00:07:25,010 --> 00:07:26,030
耐心點
Patience.

129
00:07:30,990 --> 00:07:31,980
這就是...
This...

130
00:07:37,030 --> 00:07:39,120
我期待已久的船上傳來的信息
...message I've been waiting for from the ship.

131
00:07:40,220 --> 00:07:41,670
無風
Windstille.

132
00:07:42,250 --> 00:07:44,170
"我們被困了
"We are becalmed. 

133
00:07:44,170 --> 00:07:47,600
他調查了一番  但沒有結果"
He searches, but I remain hidden."

134
00:07:49,330 --> 00:07:50,220
如果他們沒能看住他
If they fail to hold him,

135
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:51,610
他可能隨時會來
he could arrive at any time.

136
00:07:53,750 --> 00:07:55,620
你警告了瑪麗·西布里了嗎
Have you warned Mary Sibley?

137
00:07:56,010 --> 00:07:56,690
沒
No.

138
00:07:57,430 --> 00:07:58,740
她對德國人的事一無所知
She knows nothing of the Germans

139
00:07:58,740 --> 00:08:00,720
她也不知道我和他們有聯系
nor of my contact with them

140
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,690
更無法預料即將到來的威脅
nor of the impending threat.

141
00:08:02,690 --> 00:08:05,140
如果他們真有能力牽制住他
If they succeed in keeping him at bay,

142
00:08:05,150 --> 00:08:07,230
她也就沒必要知道了
then she has no need to know.

143
00:08:09,010 --> 00:08:10,900
如果他勢不可擋
And if he cannot be stopped,

144
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:13,720
游戲就又有得玩了  不是嗎
well, then it's an entirely new game, isn't it?

145
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:16,550
這可能帶來很多威脅  你不該告訴她嗎
It threatens everything. Shouldn't you tell her?

146
00:08:16,550 --> 00:08:17,960
情報就是力量
Knowledge is power.

147
00:08:18,900 --> 00:08:20,480
說到力量
And with regard to power,

148
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:23,800
如今她的力量已經足夠之多
she has more than her share at the moment,

149
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:24,960
你說是嗎
wouldn't you agree?

150
00:08:29,230 --> 00:08:31,260
你確定這么做是正確的嗎
Are you sure you've done the right thing?

151
00:08:31,270 --> 00:08:33,160
當你拉我入伙的時候  你確定嗎
Were you sure when you brought me in?

152
00:08:33,890 --> 00:08:34,730
我確定
Yes.

153
00:08:34,730 --> 00:08:36,080
我救了你的命
I saved your life.

154
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:38,500
我會一直保你平安
And I will never cease saving it.

155
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:39,330
我知道
I know.

156
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:42,360
過來
Come.

157
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:53,070
我必須找到惡靈
I must find the Malum.

158
00:08:53,070 --> 00:08:54,390
就在約翰·奧登手上
John Alden has it.

159
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:55,180
是的
Yes.

160
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:57,920
他也知道自己手握權柄
And he knows he has something of power,

161
00:08:58,560 --> 00:09:01,120
巫師們不惜性命也要奪回手中
something witches would kill and die for.

162
00:09:01,670 --> 00:09:03,410
他一定會將它藏在隱匿之處
He will have well-hidden it.

163
00:09:03,410 --> 00:09:04,910
那你要怎么找
Well, then how will you find it?

164
00:09:06,040 --> 00:09:08,570
我打算搜尋他的意識
I've a mind to search his mind.

165
00:09:08,570 --> 00:09:11,170
夢游術嗎  不行
Dream walking? No.

166
00:09:11,170 --> 00:09:12,260
一定還有別的辦法
There has to be another way.

167
00:09:12,260 --> 00:09:14,330
時間不多了  緹圖芭
We're running out of time, Tituba.

168
00:09:14,330 --> 00:09:15,960
沒有惡靈和它帶來的一切
Without the Malum and all it contains,

169
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,650
大祭典便無法完成
our grand rite is not possible.

170
00:09:18,510 --> 00:09:19,500
相信我
Trust me.

171
00:09:19,800 --> 00:09:21,730
進去之后我會立刻找到惡靈
Once inside, I'll find the Malum,

172
00:09:21,730 --> 00:09:22,560
隨即離開
and then I'll get out.

173
00:09:22,560 --> 00:09:23,730
進去
Inside?

174
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:26,670
你要進入不是房屋而是人心
It is not a house you invade but a man!

175
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:28,000
這個人還很特別
And not just any man.

176
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:32,400
你確定是為尋找惡靈  而不是只想接近他嗎
Are you sure it is the Malum you seek and not just access to him?

177
00:09:33,470 --> 00:09:35,930
不管我對約翰有何私情
Whatever my personal feelings are for John,

178
00:09:35,930 --> 00:09:37,440
我只是為了找到惡靈
I am only seeking the Malum.

179
00:09:37,450 --> 00:09:38,600
你可曾想過
Do you have any idea

180
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:40,410
闖入他的夢境之中
what crawling around inside his dreams

181
00:09:40,410 --> 00:09:42,440
對你們倆有何影響
could do to you and to him?

182
00:09:42,830 --> 00:09:45,790
這可能會損毀你們兩人的心智
It could leave either or both of you shattered,

183
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:47,570
無法分辨現實與夢境
unable to tell dreams from reality.

184
00:09:47,570 --> 00:09:49,480
你可能會迷失或者被困在夢里
You could be lost, trapped!

185
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:51,830
還有別的辦法能找到惡靈
There are other ways to find the Malum.

186
00:09:54,130 --> 00:09:55,950
說實話  我很害怕
I cannot lie. I am afraid.

187
00:09:55,950 --> 00:09:56,690
很好
Good.

188
00:09:57,180 --> 00:09:58,190
怕是好事
Be afraid.

189
00:09:58,610 --> 00:09:59,900
照看著我
Watch over me.

190
00:10:00,790 --> 00:10:02,340
但這是我的選擇
But this is my choice.

191
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,840
不管你是否幫忙  我意已決
I will do this with or without you.

192
00:10:05,980 --> 00:10:08,860
緹圖芭  現在就送我過去
Tituba, send me. Now.

193
00:10:30,970 --> 00:10:36,690
{\an8}約翰·鄧恩的詩《歌》

194
00:10:30,970 --> 00:10:33,510
流星隕落  奔走采擷
Go now. Catch a falling star.

195
00:10:34,210 --> 00:10:36,690
首烏似女  珠胎暗結
Get with child a mandrake root.

196
00:10:37,080 --> 00:10:39,470
時光逝去  穿梭而至
Travel back where past years are.

197
00:10:39,820 --> 00:10:42,420
惡魔足印  因循踏遍
Through the cloven devil's hoof.

198
00:10:42,420 --> 00:10:45,270
汝之所求  皆在其心
What you seek is in his heart.

199
00:10:45,270 --> 00:10:47,890
天使之術  現其所思
Know his thoughts through angel's art.

200
00:10:47,900 --> 00:10:49,880
巫焰燎燎  萬事皆備
As torches ever ready be,

201
00:10:50,500 --> 00:10:53,570
穿越白晝之門  一  二  三
through daylight's gate step one, two, three.

202
00:11:24,930 --> 00:11:26,730
你為什么等了這么久
Why have you waited so long?

203
00:11:54,070 --> 00:11:55,640
玩得開心嗎
Enjoying yourself?

204
00:11:56,700 --> 00:11:57,950
我還沒找到
I didn't find it yet.

205
00:12:01,410 --> 00:12:02,790
但我知道我能
But I know I can.

206
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:22,930
這片海有問題
This sea is unnatural.

207
00:12:22,930 --> 00:12:24,290
我能聞到  感覺到
I smell it. I feel it.

208
00:12:24,290 --> 00:12:27,050
我們被籠罩在黑暗的術法之中
We are under a dark enchantment.

209
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,810
我們把船搜了個遍
We have searched high and low.

210
00:12:29,810 --> 00:12:32,720
船上沒有巫師
There is no witch on this ship!

211
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:34,580
我說絕對有
And I say there is.

212
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:36,780
每個人都盤查過了
We have searched everyone.

213
00:12:37,160 --> 00:12:40,350
查了兩遍  巫師到底在哪里
Twice. So where is the witch?

214
00:12:40,950 --> 00:12:41,880
就在這里
Right here.

215
00:12:47,390 --> 00:12:49,980
繩結在哪里  船長
Where is the knot, captain?

216
00:12:57,840 --> 00:13:00,080
你的繩結藏在哪里
Where have you hidden the knot?

217
00:13:02,950 --> 00:13:05,710
那綁住了海風的繩結在哪里
Where is the knot that binds the wind?

218
00:13:06,290 --> 00:13:08,510
去死吧[德語]
Friss scheibe und stirb!

219
00:13:09,930 --> 00:13:15,080
你不會活著到達新世界的[德語]
Sie werden die neue welt nie lebend erreichen!

220
00:13:21,920 --> 00:13:22,750
我的脖子
My neck!

221
00:13:24,710 --> 00:13:26,280
掛在我脖子上
Around my neck!

222
00:13:34,210 --> 00:13:35,410
再見了[德語]
Auf wiedersehen.

223
00:13:42,660 --> 00:13:43,990
船長  起風了
Captain, the wind's up.

224
00:13:43,990 --> 00:13:45,020
船帆已經鼓滿
The sails are full.

225
00:13:47,700 --> 00:13:49,900
現在這條船歸我管
I am now master of this ship.

226
00:13:53,750 --> 00:13:56,940
告訴舵手  向西航行
Tell the helmsman due west.

227
00:13:58,890 --> 00:14:00,120
閉上眼睛
Close your eyes...

228
00:14:01,140 --> 00:14:02,340
打破一枚雞蛋
and you break an egg.

229
00:14:04,130 --> 00:14:05,840
然后想象自己的婚禮
And you imagine your wedding,

230
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:08,590
你站在教堂前面
so you're standing there in front of the meeting house

231
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:10,630
手捧鮮花
holding a bunch of flowers.

232
00:14:10,630 --> 00:14:12,190
喜鐘為你敲響
The bells are ringing for you.

233
00:14:12,570 --> 00:14:14,810
等你睜開雙眼
And then when you open your eyes,

234
00:14:14,810 --> 00:14:17,050
就能看見未來丈夫的臉
you see the face of the man you're to marry.

235
00:14:18,380 --> 00:14:20,730
但我們已經知道多莉會嫁給誰了
But we already know who Dollie'll marry.

236
00:14:22,030 --> 00:14:24,010
糟老頭喬·巴克
Stinky, old Joe Barker.

237
00:14:24,010 --> 00:14:25,210
我才不會
I will not.

238
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:27,630
但你已經和他行連理之禮了
But -- but you've already bundled with him.

239
00:14:27,640 --> 00:14:28,880
還沒有
Have not.

240
00:14:28,880 --> 00:14:30,310
馬上就要了
But you're going to.

241
00:14:30,310 --> 00:14:31,020
是的
Yes.

242
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:33,560
就在今晚
Tonight.

243
00:14:34,620 --> 00:14:36,400
一定還有其他人更適合我
There's got to be someone else for me.

244
00:14:37,240 --> 00:14:38,050
如果有
Well, if there is,

245
00:14:38,050 --> 00:14:39,460
金星之鏡會展示給你
The venus glass will show him to you.

246
00:14:40,780 --> 00:14:42,290
但你得先把茶給喝了
But first you have to drink the tea.

247
00:14:46,880 --> 00:14:47,760
全喝光
All of it.

248
00:15:35,370 --> 00:15:36,390
你看到了嗎
Did you see that?

249
00:15:36,390 --> 00:15:37,800
你看到什么了
What did you see?

250
00:15:37,810 --> 00:15:39,230
你看到喬·巴克了嗎
Did you see joe barker?

251
00:15:39,730 --> 00:15:40,790
沒有  我...
No, I...

252
00:15:43,350 --> 00:15:44,940
我不確定看到了什么  但...
I don't know what I saw, but...

253
00:15:45,350 --> 00:15:46,100
我...
I...

254
00:15:47,610 --> 00:15:48,880
我必須得走了
But I -- but I have to go now.

255
00:15:49,330 --> 00:15:51,640
我快趕不上連理儀式了
Um, I'll -- I'll be late for my bundling,

256
00:15:51,640 --> 00:15:53,520
如果破壞了這樁天賜良緣
And my mother will beat me

257
00:15:53,530 --> 00:15:56,010
母親會打死我的
for ruining a perfectly fine match.

258
00:15:57,780 --> 00:15:59,010
我們都該走了
We all should go, too.

259
00:16:09,870 --> 00:16:10,880
我做到了
I did it.

260
00:16:11,540 --> 00:16:12,900
效果就像
And it worked just --

261
00:16:13,460 --> 00:16:14,980
就像你描述的那樣
just like you said it would.

262
00:16:15,460 --> 00:16:16,970
我先給她下藥
I-I gave her the potion first,

263
00:16:16,970 --> 00:16:18,340
然后我在腦海中想象
and then I pictured it in my mind,

264
00:16:18,340 --> 00:16:20,210
她就看到了
and she saw it.

265
00:16:20,210 --> 00:16:22,200
這還只是開始
And this is just the beginning.

266
00:16:23,400 --> 00:16:26,500
下一步你要助我將塞勒姆逼入絕境
Next you will help push Salem over the edge,

267
00:16:27,070 --> 00:16:28,630
但首先
But first...

268
00:16:29,040 --> 00:16:31,530
你得學會如何讓靈魂脫離軀體
You must learn to walk wherever you will

269
00:16:32,250 --> 00:16:33,820
任意游走
without your body.

270
00:16:48,900 --> 00:16:51,680
主啊我祈求一睹你真容
I begged to see your face, lord.

271
00:16:54,610 --> 00:16:56,260
難道我面前的就是嗎
Am I looking at it now?

272
00:16:58,420 --> 00:17:00,040
人們都說發瘋的第一個征兆
They say it's the first sign of folly,

273
00:17:00,040 --> 00:17:01,560
就是自言自語
talking to oneself.

274
00:17:02,800 --> 00:17:04,840
我沒有自言自語
I wasn't talking to myself.

275
00:17:06,590 --> 00:17:07,810
我是對主祈禱
But to god.

276
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,590
或是我父親
Or my father.

277
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,720
如果這兩者有區別的話
If there is a difference.

278
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:14,500
你父親在這兒嗎
Is he here?

279
00:17:15,280 --> 00:17:16,270
更糟
Worse.

280
00:17:18,610 --> 00:17:19,470
在這兒
Here.

281
00:17:21,310 --> 00:17:22,880
看來我們并沒有想象中那么不同
I think we're not so different.

282
00:17:24,290 --> 00:17:25,650
如果不是已經有了這么多煩心事
That would worry me immensely

283
00:17:25,650 --> 00:17:28,390
聽到你這么說還真是讓我擔憂
were I not already consumed with other worries.

284
00:17:39,140 --> 00:17:42,240
顯然有些真相不能在書里找到
And apparently there are some truths not contained in books.

285
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,830
實踐
Knowledge

286
00:17:46,830 --> 00:17:50,920
才能出真知
must be tested against the anvil of experience.

287
00:17:52,490 --> 00:17:55,970
而我一直以為的真知卻在昨晚被徹底顛覆
Last night my knowledge cracked like poorly forged steel.

288
00:17:55,970 --> 00:17:56,990
聽到那個巫婆說的話之后
After what that witch said,

289
00:17:56,990 --> 00:17:59,170
我開始懷疑一切
I can be sure of nothing but my doubts.

290
00:18:00,830 --> 00:18:02,060
對所有事物
I doubt everything.

291
00:18:02,410 --> 00:18:06,490
我的書本  工具  方法
My books, my tools, my methods.

292
00:18:08,620 --> 00:18:10,000
甚至我自己
Even myself.

293
00:18:10,680 --> 00:18:12,520
那你就用自己所擁有的武器來戰斗
Then you fight with the weapons you have.

294
00:18:12,780 --> 00:18:13,540
你是指
Meaning?

295
00:18:14,030 --> 00:18:15,230
如果你滿腹疑云
If all you have is doubt,

296
00:18:16,030 --> 00:18:18,440
就讓懷疑成為你的武器
then you make doubt itself the weapon.

297
00:18:19,990 --> 00:18:21,150
你質疑一切
You question everything.

298
00:18:23,710 --> 00:18:25,030
甚至我自己
Even myself.

299
00:18:26,430 --> 00:18:28,070
尤其是你自己
Especially yourself.

300
00:18:29,060 --> 00:18:31,700
我相信主把我倆聚在一起是有理由的
I do believe god brought us together for a reason.

301
00:18:32,050 --> 00:18:33,880
為了把對方逼瘋嗎
To drive each other insane?

302
00:18:35,190 --> 00:18:35,850
不
No.

303
00:18:37,590 --> 00:18:39,940
因為彌漫在塞勒姆的陰霾需要的光明之多
'cause the shadow over Salem requires more light

304
00:18:39,940 --> 00:18:41,600
我們單獨一人都無法提供
than either of us can provide alone.

305
00:18:47,880 --> 00:18:49,920
你比任何人都更了解
You know more than anyone about...

306
00:18:52,300 --> 00:18:53,380
了解一切
Well, everything.

307
00:18:57,070 --> 00:18:59,010
你對夢境知道多少
So what do you know about dreams?

308
00:19:00,640 --> 00:19:02,800
未被發現的國度
The undiscovered country.

309
00:19:03,760 --> 00:19:04,450
什么
What?

310
00:19:04,730 --> 00:19:06,180
夢境
Dreams.

311
00:19:06,180 --> 00:19:07,830
多數人無視它
Most men dismiss them.

312
00:19:08,610 --> 00:19:10,120
但根據我的計算
But by my calculation,

313
00:19:10,130 --> 00:19:13,450
一個活滿圣經全壽命70年的人
a man who lives his full biblical span of 70 years

314
00:19:13,450 --> 00:19:18,530
會花其中的20年活在另一個夢境國度
will spend as many as 20 of them in another realm,

315
00:19:18,530 --> 00:19:20,200
在那里一切都是幻境
where nothing is as it seems.

316
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:21,710
你認為夢境是真的
So you believe they're real?

317
00:19:21,710 --> 00:19:22,800
沒錯
They are.

318
00:19:23,440 --> 00:19:25,210
我們自己的新大陸
Our own private America,

319
00:19:25,910 --> 00:19:29,720
一個充滿恐懼和愉悅的新世界
A new world filled with equal parts terror and delight.

320
00:19:31,540 --> 00:19:34,350
顯然人不需要進鬼屋也能見著鬼
Apparently one not need be a house to be haunted.

321
00:19:35,970 --> 00:19:37,070
你的意思是
What do you mean?

322
00:19:37,510 --> 00:19:39,820
你不是唯一一個擁有無數欲望
You're not the only one who knows what it feels like

323
00:19:39,820 --> 00:19:43,040
卻只能在夢中成真的人
to hold desires that come true only in dreams.

324
00:19:43,350 --> 00:19:45,130
每天早晨  我們都面臨抉擇
But every morning, we have a choice.

325
00:19:45,840 --> 00:19:47,250
忘記夢境
Forget our dreams...

326
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:50,340
或者活在夢想中
or live them.

327
00:19:53,250 --> 00:19:54,790
當我還是小姑娘的時候
My mother sewed Mr. Barker and me

328
00:19:54,790 --> 00:19:56,430
我母親把巴克先生和我縫進這個袋里
into this bag when I was a girl.

329
00:19:59,320 --> 00:20:02,090
我們談天說地  度過了愉快的夜晚
Such pleasant nights we spent talking of this and that.

330
00:20:02,990 --> 00:20:04,840
這些縫線防止你們在婚禮當晚之前
That stitch keeps you from having too much pleasure

331
00:20:04,840 --> 00:20:06,120
過度享樂
before the wedding night.

332
00:20:06,420 --> 00:20:07,700
腰部以下安分點
Nothing below the waist.

333
00:20:14,570 --> 00:20:17,680
你真的去過七角閣樓嗎
Is it true you've been in the house of seven gables?

334
00:20:17,680 --> 00:20:20,180
是的  我常去那
Oh, yes. Many times.

335
00:20:20,930 --> 00:20:22,760
我朋友梅西如今就住在那兒
My friend Mercy lives there now.

336
00:20:22,770 --> 00:20:24,940
你靠近她難道不會害怕嗎
Aren't you afraid to be close to her?

337
00:20:25,380 --> 00:20:26,100
不會
No.

338
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:31,300
那你害怕靠近我嗎
Are you afraid to be close to me?

339
00:20:53,800 --> 00:20:54,940
死丫頭
Wicked girl!

340
00:20:54,940 --> 00:20:57,140
這個睡袋見證了三代婚姻
That bag's seen three generations married!

341
00:20:57,140 --> 00:20:58,710
這事沒完  小丫頭
This isn't over, little missy!

342
00:20:58,710 --> 00:21:00,360
我會去告訴你母親的
I'll take this up with your mother!

343
00:21:23,330 --> 00:21:25,140
它在哪兒  親愛的
Where is it, my love?

344
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:28,590
告訴我它在哪兒
Show me where it is.

345
00:21:31,480 --> 00:21:33,510
我  我不明白
I-I don't understand.

346
00:21:33,840 --> 00:21:35,130
-不明白嗎  -不明白
- No? - No.

347
00:21:35,980 --> 00:21:36,850
如今這一切說明什么
What does this mean?

348
00:21:37,980 --> 00:21:39,020
你在乎嗎
Do you care?

349
00:21:39,640 --> 00:21:40,580
這是真的
It is,

350
00:21:41,390 --> 00:21:42,330
我們在一起
we are.

351
00:21:43,150 --> 00:21:44,670
你只要知道這個就夠了
That's all that matters.

352
00:21:56,150 --> 00:21:57,660
這樣足夠真實了嗎
Real enough for you?

353
00:22:03,140 --> 00:22:04,340
還是這樣
Or this?

354
00:22:07,170 --> 00:22:09,120
我得知道它在哪兒
I need to know where it is.

355
00:22:09,340 --> 00:22:10,190
什么
What?

356
00:22:15,640 --> 00:22:17,050
{\an8}吉爾斯·科里

357
00:22:29,880 --> 00:22:31,060
我找到惡靈了
I found the Malum.

358
00:22:31,990 --> 00:22:33,410
就在科里的墳墓里
It's in Corey's grave.

359
00:22:33,690 --> 00:22:36,230
奧登把它藏在了科里的墳墓里
Alden has hidden it in Corey's grave.

360
00:22:36,970 --> 00:22:38,320
我警告過你的
I warned you.

361
00:22:38,780 --> 00:22:41,440
進入任何人的夢境都十分危險
Dream walking in any man is dangerous,

362
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,890
更別說是你愛的人了
let alone one that you love.

363
00:22:43,950 --> 00:22:46,060
你可能會徹底地迷失其中再也出不來了
You could lose your way and never come back.

364
00:22:46,770 --> 00:22:48,370
別再進入那人的夢境了
Keep out of that man's head.

365
00:23:20,270 --> 00:23:22,640
那小婊子撕爛了我曾祖母的連理睡袋
Little bitch tore my great-gran's bundling bag.

366
00:23:22,640 --> 00:23:24,690
你那個有口臭的兒子
And your stink-breathed boy

367
00:23:24,690 --> 00:23:26,570
在你的寶貝睡袋上戳了個洞
poked a hole in your precious bag,

368
00:23:26,570 --> 00:23:28,530
還想在我女兒身上戳一個
tried to poke one in my girl!

369
00:23:28,530 --> 00:23:29,600
那個睡袋上
There's no holes in that bag

370
00:23:29,600 --> 00:23:31,240
只有她逃走時撕開的洞
but the ones she tore running out.

371
00:23:31,240 --> 00:23:34,130
誰會相信你們巴克家說的話
And who'd believe you or any Barker?

372
00:23:34,240 --> 00:23:35,910
看見沒  親愛的  起作用了
See, my dear? It's working.

373
00:23:35,910 --> 00:23:37,710
誰都知道你們是一伙騙子
Everyone knows you're a pack of liars

374
00:23:37,710 --> 00:23:40,310
靠著欺騙我們大家才發家致富
and cheats getting rich off the rest of us.

375
00:23:40,310 --> 00:23:42,470
你要是不停止侮辱我們家族
You stop talking filth about my family

376
00:23:42,470 --> 00:23:44,120
我就讓你不能再說話
or I'll stop you talking.

377
00:23:47,520 --> 00:23:49,530
笑什么笑  小賤人
What are you laughing at, you little minx?!

378
00:23:50,900 --> 00:23:52,730
巴克一族就算是烏合之眾
Those Barkers may be a foul lot,

379
00:23:52,730 --> 00:23:53,900
但是他們富得流油
but they have money enough,

380
00:23:53,900 --> 00:23:55,750
配你這樣的貨色已經是綽綽有余了
and it was a fine match for the likes of you,

